      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SLICK SAND (1) was game in defeat at the latest run, finishing second and beaten a nose (23.04) behind Extreme Blue at this track. Must come into calculations. MODEST MAN (4) slotted in just off the lead from the wide draw last start and boxed on to finish third (25.38) at Grafton in a NG over 450m. Has a strong record out of this box with two wins and two minor placings from five starts. Expected to be in the finish again. LIPSCHITZ (3) broke from the inside draw and filled a minor placing last start, beaten only 0.8 lengths (17.62) behind Federal Mercury at Taree Super Track. Hard to beat again. SUNSHINE RHONDA (2) gets a chance to redeem an unplaced effort here last start.",
